description: An easy (and very tasty) pie - perfect for a cold winter's night!
name: Cheese Chicken & Bacon Pies Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place pies on baking paper lined baking tray and brush pastry with beaten egg using pastry brush. Sprinkle with sesame seeds if desired. Place in oven and cook for 25-30 minutes or until golden brown.
